"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.6.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.6.2</span> 標題：雕刻的（石）像（graven [stone] image）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： אֶבֶן, מַשְׂכִּית</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ’even maskith)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1\">LEV 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:52\">NUM 33:52</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： פָּסִיל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： pasil)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:5\">DEU 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:25\">DEU 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:3\">DEU 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:19\">JDG 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:26\">JDG 3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:41\">2KI 17:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:19\">2CH 33:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:22\">2CH 33:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:4\">2CH 34:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:7\">2CH 34:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:58\">PSA 78:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:10\">ISA 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:9\">ISA 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:22\">ISA 30:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:8\">ISA 42:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:19\">JER 8:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:38\">JER 50:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:47\">JER 51:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:52\">JER 51:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:2\">HOS 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:7\">MIC 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:12\">MIC 5:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： פֶּסֶל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： pesel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:4\">EXO 20:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1\">LEV 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:16\">DEU 4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:23\">DEU 4:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:25\">DEU 4:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:8\">DEU 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:15\">DEU 27:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:3\">JDG 17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:4\">JDG 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:14\">JDG 18:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:17\">JDG 18:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:18\">JDG 18:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:20\">JDG 18:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:30\">JDG 18:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:31\">JDG 18:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:7\">2KI 21:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:7\">2CH 33:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:7\">PSA 97:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:19\">ISA 40:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:20\">ISA 40:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:17\">ISA 42:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:9\">ISA 44:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:10\">ISA 44:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:15\">ISA 44:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:17\">ISA 44:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:20\">ISA 45:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:5\">ISA 48:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:14\">JER 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:17\">JER 51:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:14\">NAM 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18\">HAB 2:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： γλυπτός</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： gluptos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:17\">WIS 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis15:13\">WIS 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:68\">1MA 5:68</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0463_stone_image.jpg\" alt=\"亞捫人神靈的頭像（公元前8世紀晚期）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">亞捫人神靈的頭像（公元前8世紀晚期） (Gary Todd, Israel Museum, CC0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>雕刻的像是用木頭或石頭雕刻而成的偶像，這些像的大小和形狀有很大差別。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>這些像是雕刻或塑形而成的。關於翻譯的其他注意事項，參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.6.3 鑄像 (molten image)&lt;REALIA:4.6.3&gt;</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
